{
  "stem": "27150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know-- [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a sort of a bar mitzvah, not, not the ones they're having here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you see, that we went to-- went-- that means I didn't learn to the bar-- didn't have to learn to the bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took me down to the schul, and the thing was telling me, and I was repeating, one after the other.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, that means what was from the [INAUDIBLE] I could read, you know and what was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the holy book, you see.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That means, I was repeating after the cantor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Repeat after me-- [HEBREW] et cetera.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it was a bit of a farce.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know, maybe [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you see, because my father was in Moscow during the revolution, and he said that if I have seen things, you see, that means that God is not existing.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And once we caught father, you see, smoking a cigar on Yom Kippur, you see, and having a feast, while we were playing football, and mama was sitting in the ladies' compartment, you know.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And everything-- you can't smoke on Shabbos, but not on the balcony, so the bottom neighbors don't see you, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, you see, there were three newspapers in Yiddish and two newspapers in Polish, you see, edited and read by the Jews.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were a few magazines.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, there was about two Yiddish theaters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were sort of silly play, operettas, or something like this, you see.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means, we recently read memoirs of [INAUDIBLE], you see, and comedies, and historic plays, musicals and dramas, and very good translations.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, now, the Jews took part, very big part, in Polish culture.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
